Revolvers are kind of our jam.

I know you all like some nice custom build wheelgun stuff far from standard - just received a new @hogueinc custom big butt grip for my @smithandwessoninc open 627-8 blaster build by @gundoctor1911 
This grip is the perfect addition to that gun - aggressive burner strips to the side of the backstrap, beautiful dragon 🐉 skin texture on the sides and the hogue wordmark on the front - perfectly shaped to fit exactly my grip - pure awesomeness in a really striking 🤩 color scheme! Love it! 😍

node.text:
Big shoutout to RECOIL for reviewing our new Action Enhancement Kit for the CZ P-10.

PC: @recoilmagazine ⬅️👍
・・・
Apex Tactical has for years been a reliable choice for individuals who want aftermarket triggers in their handguns, starting with the Smith & Wesson M&P series in the early 2010’s. Since then, they have engineered and released quality triggers for most well-known striker-fired handguns in the industry, and their expansion continues. The CZ-P10c and P10f were both praised at their release for quality triggers and ergonomics. This didn’t stop Apex from improving on an already great platform. Thus, the CZ-P10c/P10f Action Enhancement Kit. Full article on RecoilWeb.com, link in bio.

node.text:
#Hellacious

PC:  @methreview ⬅️👍
・・・
The Springfield Hellcat has been my new EDC gun for a few months now... This thing rocks!

Currently I run it without the RMSc because I don't particularly care for the sight.... I'd love to get a @swampfoxoptics sentinel for it soon. The 15RD mags give me the same capacity as my M&P 2.0 4" compact in a much smaller and lighter package. 

The #Apex Trigger gives me much more positive control of the gun and is a must have on the hellcat in my opinion. I installed it in like 30 minutes following along with their video. Thank you @apextactical 

Also... The @crkt_knives  Clever Girl is one badass knife.

node.text:
Representing The Valley

PC: @sonorandefense ⬅️👍
・・・
Huge shoutout to our friends at @apextactical for inviting us over for a meet & greet, shop tour, and demo of the brand new CZ P-10 trigger - as well as enhanced mag catch and slide stop! 

I’m sure you already know, but those are true gentlemen and industry leading engineers. The amount of detailed R&D, safety testing, and quality assurance that goes into their products really shows you why no one in the industry can touch them. 

I’ve been running Apex triggers since long before we started SDT, in my first Gen M&P’s. Grateful to have such a great group of guys here in the valley. 

With all of that said, we are going to work on ramping up the R&D on our side to try and finalize some stipple options for the CZ P-10 models. We may be taking a hard look at the FN 509 series as well, but no ETA’s at this time. 

Did you get in on the P-10 trigger pre-order?? 

#cz #czp10 #apex #apextactical  #apextrigger #wdtr #apexthatczp10 #az #arizona #madeinarizona #peoriaaz #pewpew

node.text:
New CZ P-10 trigger kit in action.

PC: @amy.556 ⬅️👍👍
・・・
Testing the new @apextactical Action Enhancement Kit for the 9mm P-10 C, S & F from CZ. Available for pre-order.  The kit contains:

A) Apex Action Enhancement Trigger
B) Apex Performance Disconnector
C) Apex Slide Cover Plate

There are two distinct trigger pull options based on which disconnector you choose to install.

Option #1) Sub-4.0 lbs trigger pull with a light, smooth take-up and linear rolling trigger break at striker release, plus a reduction in over-travel.

Option #2) 5.5 lbs, keeping the CZ factory disconnector. Provides a more defined trigger break at striker release.

Thanks at @sava_nez for letting me test this out and for lending me you @tier1concealed holster. 

#czp10 #apextactical #billdrill #apextrigger #wdtr #apexthatczp10 #czusa #czp10f #pewpew
